  v 2 get T 9 get mul add
  v 3 get T 13 get mul add
  
  v 0 get T 2 get mul
  v 1 get T 6 get mul add
  v 2 get T 10 get mul add
  v 3 get T 14 get mul add
  
  v 0 get T 3 get mul
  v 1 get T 7 get mul add
  v 2 get T 11 get mul add
  v 3 get T 15 get mul add
]
end } def

